This is a placeholder for the raylib static library.

To build raylib for Linux:
1. Download raylib source from https://github.com/raysan5/raylib
2. Install dependencies: sudo apt-get install libx11-dev libxrandr-dev libxinerama-dev libxcursor-dev libxi-dev
3. Build: make PLATFORM=PLATFORM_DESKTOP
4. Copy src/libraylib.a to this directory

Or use CMake:
mkdir build && cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
make
cp src/libraylib.a ..
